title.narrative: Economic Growth PASA - E3/ED, E3/EP, E3/TRR, E3/LS and E3/PLC

description.narrative: (USAID Economic Growth, Education and Environment (E3)): .This Participating Agency Service Agreement (PASA) will continue to provide services with the U.S. Department of Agriculture (USDA) to allow E3 office to carry out key Agency functions and responsibilities. Under the PASA, USDA provides technical expertise to perform technical assistance, training, and information in the areas of education and training, economic growth, and program support. This PASA provides technically qualified and experienced professionals who can assist in: providing technical leadership and field support; supporting evaluation, research, learning and outreach, cultivating local development partners implementing pioneering programs; and building Agency expertise. .. .. .
